long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Pro Blocker: The Ultimate Ad-Blocking Tool. Block Ads on YouTube, Facebook, and All Websites for Free!

Pro Blocker is built with one mission: to eliminate every ad so you can focus solely on the content you care about.

Features
Blocks all ads on every website, including Facebook and YouTube
Prevents malware and online tracking
Boosts your browser’s performance by removing intrusive content
No "acceptable ads" or ad network whitelists

Pro Blocker is a free extension that blocks all kinds of ads—whether they're banner, text, or video ads—and keeps you safe by stopping malicious websites known to spread malware. It also disables tracking systems that try to follow your activity across the web. With advanced filtering, Pro Blocker ensures you enjoy a clean, uninterrupted experience across all sites, including YouTube and Facebook.

What sets Pro Blocker apart from other ad blockers like AdGuard, Adblock, or Adblock Plus?

Unlike other ad blockers, Pro Blocker doesn’t allow “acceptable ads” or maintain a whitelist where advertisers can pay to bypass the filters. We believe in blocking all ads for a faster and cleaner browsing experience. Blocking everything also results in better browser performance, improving CPU efficiency and reducing memory usage—giving you a smoother, faster internet experience compared to other popular solutions like AdGuard, Adblock, Adblock Plus, and even uBlock in certain benchmarks.

Pro Blocker also gives you the freedom to support websites you trust by selectively allowing ads—it’s entirely your choice!

How does Pro Blocker protect your privacy?

Your privacy is our top priority. Pro Blocker includes a powerful Privacy Filter to block an extensive range of online trackers that try to monitor your online behavior. We make sure your browsing history stays private, just as it should.

How does Pro Blocker shield you from online threats?

Pro Blocker blocks domains that are notorious for distributing malware. This ensures you are protected from viruses, spyware, and other malicious software while you browse. With Pro Blocker, your risk of infection while surfing the web is greatly reduced.

Benefits of using Pro Blocker:
Enhance browser speed
Improve page load times
Reduce memory usage on the pages you visit
Save bandwidth

Pro Blocker gives you control over your browsing experience. Block ads, safeguard your privacy, and keep your computer safe—all for free!
